<hymn_number>312</hymn_number>
<title>ʿạrfk msẖ qạdr trtạḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ʿạrfk msẖ qạdr trtạḥ .. sẖạyf qlbk klh jrạḥ)2
 ʿmrk fy ṭryq mẓlm rạḥ .. (tʿạl yswʿ ʿndh ạlạ̉frạḥ)2
 ạlqrạr- (tʿạl ạ̹lyh wslm lyh .. wḥṭ ḥyạtk byn ạ̹ydyh
 hạygẖfr lyk kẖṭạyạ mạḍyk .. wyḍmn kl ạlḥạḍr fyh)2
 2- (whạtfḍl ʿạysẖ tʿbạn .. ṭwl mạ ʿynyk ʿly̱ ạlạ̹nsạn)2
 lyh fkrk sẖạrd ḥyrạn .. (dh yswʿ ymlạ ạlfkr ṭmạn)2
 3- (ạ̹rjʿ wạrmy ʿạlm fạny .. msẖ hạtfkr trjʿ tạny)2
 lyh qlbk m ạlhm yʿạny .. (ʿmrk ḍạyʿ wạnt ạljạny)2
 4- (jrḥk myn yqdr ydạwyh .. dẖnbk myn yqdr ydạryh)2
 lyh kẖạyf ttqdm lyh .. (ḥmlk ạ̹rmyh klh ʿlyh)2</lyrics>
</song>